      "text": "Ir Dans un Jawans /\nMëusals wedde us taweem Tir-\ngeem istaiſitu Dſelsi/ Kasija un\nKalins / ta btja tawa Prezze-\nfchana.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 20,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Deedans prezzejahs ar te-\nwin ar ſkaisteem Wadmaleem\npar Sehdefli.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 21,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Arabija un wiſſi Leeli-\nKungt no Reedara tee prezzejahs\nzaur tawu Rohku ar Ichreen un\nAuneem un Ahscheem / ar teem\nprezzejahs tee ar tewim.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 22,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tee Prezzineeki no Sa-\nbas un Raïnas/ tee biia tawi\nBrezzineeki / wiſſadu dahrgu\nSahli/DahrgusAkminius unSel-\ntu/ nolikke tee tawôs Tirgôs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 23,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Arans un Kanne un Ge-\ndens/ tee Prezzineeki no Seebas\nAffura un Kilnada prezzejahs\nar tewim.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 24,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tee biia tawi Prezztneeki\nar tahm wiſſudahrgakahm Lee-\ntahin/ar dahrga Madunala Bak-\nkeem no pasila istakfita Dar-\nba / un ar ſkaisteem Mantu\nSchkirsteem / kas ar Auſleem\nJuſcitt/ un ſtarp Zeedru-Rohſeem\nlikti tawôs Tirgôs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 25,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tahs Latwas no Tarsis\nirr tahs angſtakas pee tewim bi-\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 26,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tawi Latwineeki irr tewi\nwarrendô Uhdenis weddutcht/\ntas Rihta Webſch irr tewi pas-\ntreezis Juhras Widdû.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 27,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tawa Manta un tawas\nPrezzes/ un tawa Prezzefchana/\ntawi Latwineeki un tawi Stuhr-\nmanni/ un tawi Latwas Patal-\nfitaji/ kas ar tewim Prezzeſcha-\nnu dſenn/ un wiſſi tawi Karra-\nWihti/ kas eekſch tewini ur/ un\nwiſſa tawa Draudse/ kas tawa\nWiddû irr/ krittihs Juhras Wid-\ndû / tawas Bohjá-Gefchanas\nDeená.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 28,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Mo tahs Brehtchanas\nBalfs tawi Latwineeku / dreb-\nbehß tee Breekſch-Pillsfahti.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 29,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un wiſſi Irrejt/ Stuhr-\nmanni/ ar wiſſeem Juhras Lat-\nwineefeem/ nokahps no tawahn\nLatwahn/ un poſtahivehs wirs\nSemines.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 30,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un tee liks tawu Balfi\npahr tewi dsirdeht/ un gauschi\nkleegß/ un mettihs Pihschlus us\nfawahn Galiwahn/ tee wahrti-\nfees Pelnds.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 31,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tee darriſees tewis deht\nPleitus/ un apjoſſihs Maiſus/\nun raudahs pahr tewi ar Dweh-\nfeles Ruhktuimu/ un gauschu\nNoscheblumu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 32,
